This repository wraps the Cell-Based-Layout-Compaction engine originally authored by:

  Ameer M.S. Abdelhadi
  https://github.com/AmeerAbdelhadi/Cell-Based-Layout-Compaction

The upstream Perl compaction script (vendor/cellCompaction.pl) retains its original
copyright and license notice as distributed by the author. No modifications are made
to the upstream source code. The script is invoked unmodified via subprocess.

This wrapper framework (src/, scripts/, docker/, configs/, data/demo/) is independent
original work and is not derived from the upstream source.

